snippet.title: Dedalium | Official Trailer 2022
snippet.description:
Dedalium is a browser extension that turns any website into an RPG game. Play and conquer the Internet!
Start your journey 👉👉 https://bit.ly/3nMEbpj

Are you worthy to own a Network Guardian? Play Dedalium, the free role - playing game!

Play while browsing the internet with Dedalium! Everything is now a Game! 

Gather objects, fight your friends on their social networks and improve your Network Guardian to be feared!
